<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="bd-section bd-section-white" id="bd-faq">
  <div class="bd-faq-inner">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p class="bd-faq-intro">Everything you need to know about ordering custom card holder stickers from BIG DAWGS.</p>

    <details>
      <summary>What file format should I use for my artwork?</summary>
      <div class="bd-faq-answer">We accept <strong>GIF, JPG, and PNG files only</strong>. For best results, upload at 300 DPI or higher with a transparent background. If your artwork is in a different format, email us before ordering and we'll work with you to find a solution.</div>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>How long does production and shipping take?</summary>
      <div class="bd-faq-answer">Most orders ship within 5–7 business days after artwork is approved. We move fast because we know you need these for your shop, show schedule, or breaks. Rush inquiries are welcome — just note it in the order.</div>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>What's the minimum order quantity?</summary>
      <div class="bd-faq-answer">Minimums vary by holder type and size. One Touch: Small starts at 25, Medium at 20, Large at 15. Toploader: Small at 30, Medium at 25, Large at 20. Prices start at $6 and go up from there. See full pricing when you configure your order.</div>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>What's the difference between holographic and cracked ice finishes?</summary>
      <div class="bd-faq-answer">Holographic stickers have a full rainbow color-shifting effect — the whole sticker changes color as the light angle shifts. Cracked ice has a unique fractured, shattered-ice pattern that gives a more textured, layered look. Both are premium; they're just totally different visual styles.</div>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Can I order stickers for both One Touch and Toploader holders?</summary>
      <div class="bd-faq-answer">Yes — just place a separate order for each holder type. The product configurator walks you through each one independently so you get exactly the right specs for both.</div>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Will the sticker damage my card holder?</summary>
      <div class="bd-faq-answer">No. Our stickers are <strong>100% residue-free</strong> — peel them off cleanly without leaving any adhesive behind on the plastic surface. They're sized to fit cleanly without covering the cardholder window or locking mechanism, so your holder functions exactly as designed.</div>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Do you work with first-time buyers?</summary>
      <div class="bd-faq-answer">Absolutely. Most of our customers are first-timers. We walk you through the artwork process, confirm everything looks right before printing, and make sure you're happy before we ship.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

